Package gw.api.databuilder

Class WorkStatusBuilder

java.lang.Object
gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<WorkStatus,WorkStatusBuilder>
gw.api.databuilder.CCDataBuilder<WorkStatus,WorkStatusBuilder>
gw.api.databuilder.WorkStatusBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
DelegateDataBuilder<WorkStatus>, ValueGenerator<WorkStatus>
public class WorkStatusBuilder extends CCDataBuilder<WorkStatus,WorkStatusBuilder>
Work status is an array on EmploymentData, which in turn is a sub object of a Claim or Exposure. Because EmploymentData can be associated with either a Claim or Exposure, and is used in several different places in the UI, there is no UI ready builder for either EmploymentData or WorkStatus
